(Yes, because i think Ha tinh is one of the most beautiful country in Viet Nam with nice weather, senic views like beach and mountains, people are very friendly, they always welcome tourists with a smile on their face. Additionally, country has rich cultural value with many festivals and heritages. So i really want more people to travel over my country. This helps to develop local tourism. Finally, bring about/out more money and jobs for local people. 


