                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is your favorite dish?
-> My favourite dish is Pho. Pho is one of the most famous tranditional food in Viet Nam. Pho is very delicious and healthy. A bow of Pho on the morning can make my day.
How to make Pho ?.
-> First, we need to prepare the ingredients like rice noodles, beaf, pork, chicken, broth, ... then we stew some broth to make the soup. after that chop the chicken, slice the beaf, put all of them together in pot. wait 20 minutes then pour it into the bow with noodle. You can add pepper and chilly to make it savourier. Let's enjoy the dish together.

